John W. BROWN and Joseph Landon, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6488. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Sept. 2, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed; mandate forthwith.
